WEBVTT

00:01:58.140 --> 00:02:03.360
what would an authentic,
deep apology be like?

00:02:08.179 --> 00:02:11.702
So, something strange began to happen.

00:02:12.404 --> 00:02:14.282
I began to write,

00:02:14.306 --> 00:02:17.290
and my father's voice
began to come through me.

00:02:18.235 --> 00:02:20.782
He began to tell me what he had done

00:02:20.806 --> 00:02:22.245
and why.

00:02:22.269 --> 00:02:25.104
He began to apologize.

00:02:25.128 --> 00:02:27.589
My father is dead almost 31 years,

00:02:27.613 --> 00:02:29.361
and yet, in this apology,

00:02:29.385 --> 00:02:31.977
the one I had to write for him,